{ White has created an annoying pin and has forked Black's knight and rook. What to do? }
16... g5 17. Nxd6 Bxd6
{ So far everything is under control - Black is about to win two light pieces for a rook. }
18. Ne6 { Last chance. } 18... Qd7
{ Very precise as  18...fxe6  would alllow  19.Qg6+ } 19. Nxg5 hxg5 20. Bxg5
Nbd5
{ Black is about to consolidate the position - two light pieces are stronger than the rook with two pawns. }
