9... a5 10. e4
{ With the inclusion of a3 and ...a5 protecting the b4 square, this might be an option for White to consider. The plan is to chase away the knight from the center and continue with Be3 and d4. }
10... Nxc3 11. bxc3 a4 { Black fixes the weakness on b3. } 12. d4 Bb3 13. Qd3
