{ And just like that, Black has hunted down the white queen - there are no good squares to retreat! }
15. Qh5+
{ or  15.Qg3  Bd6  and the fork will be executed either via d4 or f4 square. }
15... g6 16. Qh6
{ The white queen has seemingly escaped from those terrible forks... } 16...
Ncxe3 17. fxe3 Bxe3 { Beautiful geometry! } *

