{ If White doesn't react to the a-pawn's movement with either the exchange sacrifice or reroute the knight to c5, the queenside is effectively closed for business. }
11... Bf6
{ Black makes sure that White can't sacrifice the exchange on c6 anymore and protects the e5 pawn. }
