10... Nb6
{ The knight on b6 also stands pretty good and has the potential to land on c4. }
11. Nb5 O-O 12. Bc7
{ 12.Nc7  Rb8  13.Nb5  forces repetition of the position but the engines think that Black can even sacrifice an exchange for a great compensation after  12...Be6!? }
12... Qd7 { White's attack has run out of gas. } 13. Bxb6 axb6 14. Rc1 Ra5
{ Black starts to take over while White's entire kingside is sleeping. } *

