17. Nc7
{ Black has just sacrificed a piece for two pawns and intends to capture the stranded white knight. What happens if it tries to escape immediately? }
17... Bc4
{ Black cuts off the escape route via the b5 square and significantly slows down White's development. Black's ... Ng6 to trade off the dark-squared bishop appears to be already decisive. }
