{ Now ...Nc6 is a big threat so the game suddenly becomes very tactical with Black being on top of it. }
10. Bg5 Qb6
{ Very accurate - Black gets rid of the pin and also is threatening with both ...Nc6 and ...Bxc3 with ...Qb2. }
