12. g4
{ White is playing ambitiously at the kingside with intentions to play for space advantage but also weakening some squares in the process, but there is hardly anything better. If allowed, Black will play the traditional ...h6 next and secure against both g5 threats and create an outpost on h7 for his bishop. }
