{ White can't take the pawn on e4 as the knight on h3 is under attack. } 19.
Nf4 Rae8 20. Qd4 Qc5
{ Black trades off the queens. Now after  21.Rd1  Qxd4  22.Rxd4  Bxf4  ,  followed by ...Bc6, Black can start to convert the material advantage. }
