11... Rb8 { Black wins a lot of nice free tempi. } 12. Qa6 Rb6 13. Qa4 e4 14.
Ne5 Qb8
{ Black has more than enough compensation for the pawn and has the initiative. The white pawn on b2 is weak, the white queen on a4 is misplaced and can be used to win several important tempi, and the bishop on g2 is completely out of the game. }
