9... Ne5 10. Bb5+ Ke7
{ And no - this is not the Bongcloud! White can't save the pawn on d3 because of the incoming ...Nf3+ and ...Bh3 mate! And then there's the ...a6 threat. This is why the text move is so much better than  10...Bd7 }
11. O-O a6 { The bishop appears to be trapped! } 12. Ba4 exd3 13. Nf4 b5
{ White is suffering huge material losses and he's unable to exploit the walking of the black king. }
