11... O-O-O { Because of the pin, the pawn on e4 can't be touched. } 12. Be3
exd3
{ Black can be a little ambitious with other moves like  12...Ng4   or  12...Bc5  as well, but this one immediately gives Black a fine game. }
13. Bxa7 dxe2 14. Qxe2 Qxe2 15. Nxe2 Be7 { The position is about equal. } *

