{ This is what Giri played against Svidler in one of the online super tournaments in 2020, but specifically here it might not be the best. }
13. b4 a5 14. bxa5
{ White here appears to have some pressure and the opened queenside should be in White's favor as Black is underdeveloped at the moment. }
