{ Hammer,J @@StartBracket@@2621@@EndBracket@@ -Giri,A @@StartBracket@@2785@@EndBracket@@ Moscow FIDE GP 2017, now a logical continuation for White would be to trade the queens. }
14. Qxe5 Bxe5 15. Be3
{ Black has a slightly unpleasant position due to some weaknesses at the queenside. }
