14. Bb2 { What is the best reaction to the Bishop's x-ray on the queen? } 14...
Bg6
{ An important accuracy - Black remains tactically alert to his opponents' ideas.   14...Qe6?!  Why this natural move, dodging a potential discovered attack, is a mistake?  15.b5  15...c5  16.Rxf5!  The point! White sacrifices an exchange for a pawn, opening his bishops.  16...Qxf5  17.Nxe4  Nxe4  18.Bxe4  Qh5  Even though Black has the exchange, the bishop pair is dictating the pace of the game. }
