13. g4
{ This would be an attempt to stop Black's idea but White won't have one for himself. }
13... Bxg2 14. Nxg2 Nd8 15. Ne3 Ne6
{ Black is about to reroute the knight from h7 to g6 and a nice control of some of the critical squares. }
