9. Bg5
{ This seems to be the most sensible move in the position which gives White enough time to finish the development. }
9... Nbd7 10. Ne2
{ Developing the knight on  f3  10.Nf3  would allow Black to continue with  10...h6  and force the trade on f6 as bishop retreat to f4 would be met by ...Nxe4, with ...Re8 next.   Also, it's important to note that  10.Qxd6  meets a nice tactical shot  10...Nxe4! }
