9. Bf4
{ White would like to trade the pawns and then claim the center with d4, backed by two bishops. What's the most active way to meet it? }
9... Re8
{ The correct answer is - nothing! Ignore it as there are far more important things to pay attention to. Focus on White's own weaknesses, most notably on c4. }
10. Ne2 c5 11. Qd3
