c6 7. Ne2
{ If White would position the knight on f3,  then after  7.Nf3  e4  8.Nd4  instead of pushing forward the d-pawn Black can focus on the c4 pawn instead with  8...d6  ,  followed by ...c5 and ...Nc6. }
