{ Black already is thinking about ways to take over. Be warned - it involves a pawn sacrifice @@StartBracket@@again!@@EndBracket@@ Gashimov,V @@StartBracket@@2740@@EndBracket@@ -Gelfand,B @@StartBracket@@2750@@EndBracket@@ Amber-rapid 19th 2010. }
