11. Bf4
{ White is attacking the pawn on c7 with a tempo, and also dxe4 now becomes available. If White would have continued here with   11.Qc2  ,  then the simple  11...Bf5  would finish the development for Black, but the queen can be rerouted to e6 with the same ...Bh3 idea. }
