17... exf3 18. exf3 Qf6 19. Bd4 Qg6
{ After some trades at the e-file, the arising endgame is equal but it might be a little easier to play with Black. Gratka,K @@StartBracket@@2307@@EndBracket@@-Jaracz,P @@StartBracket@@2521@@EndBracket@@ Polanica Zdroj op 2001. }
