Bf5 12. b3 a5
{ You'll come to appreciate this move! Almost always the inclusion of ...a5 and a4 favors Black. }
13. a4 Ne5
{ Now it's time to reroute the knight and here in particular the e5 square looks more active than b8. Nobody is forcing Black to trade on d5. }
