[FEN "r1b1r1k1/ppp2ppp/2n2n2/3q4/4p3/2P3P1/P1NPPPBP/R1BQ1RK1 w - - 0 11"]
[SetUp "1"]

11. h3
{ Black's main idea is to play ...Qh5 and trade-off the light-squared bishops with ...Bh3. What happens if White tries to stop it? }
11... Qh5 12. g4
{ White is outright provoking Black to sacrifice.   12.Kh2  Ne5  Doesn't look fun for White but already was necessary. }
12... Bxg4 13. hxg4 Nxg4 14. Re1 { Now Black delivers quite an easy mate. }
14... Qh2+ 15. Kf1 Qh4
{ The white king stands no chance while the other white pieces are helpless. }
