{ Ginsburg,M @@StartBracket@@2381@@EndBracket@@-Kraai,J @@StartBracket@@2412@@EndBracket@@ Arthur Dake Int 1999, this is a huge mistake, and Black could have punished White right away. }
10... exd4 11. cxd4 Nxd4
{ White has no choice - now several forced moves follow. } 12. Nxd4 Rd8 13. Be3
