10... Bxe3
{ Let's keep things simple - White is going to push forward the d-pawn but it's not a problem. I suggest keeping a close look to your light-square management. It's not a good idea having ...h6 already included as after the bishop trade and following d4 you might feel that the suggested f6 seriously weakens the light squares around your king. If that happens, you can postpone the trade on e3 indefinitely. }
11. fxe3 Bd7
{ Black has a wonderful plan to reroute the knight to d6 and a very solid position. }
