20... Rxf3 { The motif of this puzzle is - intermezzo check! } 21. Bxf3 Nd4
{ White has under attack both the queen and the bishop. } 22. Bb7
{ Oops! Did you miss this move?   22.Qxg6  Nxf3+  The intermezzo.  23.Kh1  hxg6  Black has a technically winning position - the two light pieces dominate the rook. }
22... Nf3+
{ If you did not, congratulations! You are well aware of your opponent's defensive possibilities. }
23. Kh1
{ The knight can't be taken as the white queen would be left unguarded. } 23...
