23... Qb6 24. Re8+ Kh7 { White's attack is over. } 25. Qd4 Qb1+ 26. Kf2 Nd3+
{ White had nothing better than to simplify the position. } 27. Qxd3+ Qxd3 28.
Be4+ Qxe4 29. Rxe4 Be6
{ Black kept the extra piece which was eventually converted into a win in Izeta Txabarri,F  @@StartBracket@@2505@@EndBracket@@-Gomez Esteban,J @@StartBracket@@2475@@EndBracket@@ Elgoibar 09th 1999. I have to admit that the entire idea is interesting but specifically, here it brings White only trouble. Maybe under different circumstances it could work so this is something that Black should be aware of. }
