{ This is an interesting novelty and somebody is going to play it sooner or later. I'll just add that  11.h4  with a similar idea doesn't work as Black can just grab the pawn with  11...Qxe5+  12.Kd2  Qf4+  and play ...d6 next with a safe position. }
