{ This has already been played in practice and is probably the most human attempt to trick Black. Now the pawn on e5 yet again is taboo due to Kd2 and Re1. }
11... d6
{ You should be already familiar with this temporary pawn sacrifice - Black is fine to give up a pawn to castle short and attack along the e-file. }
