Qc8 15. Bxf8
{ It's not mandatory but it's not clear what are the alternatives. The black rook would otherwise go to d8 and the white pawns on c4 and c3 are quite vulnerable, and then there's the ...b5 threat. }
15... Qxf8 16. Kb2 b5
