Qa3+ 20. Kd2
{ The logical retreat - after  20.Kc2  Qxa2+  21.Kc1  Ra4  Black wins back the sacrificed material with interest. }
20... Ra4 21. Bc4
{ This allows Black to open even more files with a spectacular shot. } 21... d5
22. exd6 Rxc4 23. Qxc4 Qb2+
{ White will lose something. Now  24.Qc2  is met by  24...Re2+ } 24. Kd3 Be4+
25. Qxe4 Qa3+
{ White loses the queen. After  26.Kd2  Rxe4  27.dxc7  White gets mated with  27...Qb2+  28.Kd3  Qe2+  ,  followed by ...Rc4+ and a ladder. }
