19. Qxd7 { A free pawn? The white pawn on c5 is not hanging anymore. } 19...
Bxg2
{ It is not, but something else is! White suddenly is in a lot of trouble as  20.Bxg2  loses due to  20...Qxc4  and a double threat of ...Qc2+ and just taking the dark-squared bishop on f4. }
20. Qxe6 fxe6 21. Bxg2 Rxf4
{ White is in trouble - now  22.Kxb3  is a very risky move due to  22...Rb8+  23.Ka4  Bc3  and many threats, starting with ...Rxc4+. }
