21. Bc4
{ Black has a very dangerous attack - how will you proceed here?   21.Qxd7  This is an alternative but Black has a reply to this as well.  21...Re7!  22.Qd8+  Kg7  Among other threats, Black has an idea to play ...Qb4+ and trap the white queen with ... Ra8. }
21... d5 { Black should open the position to get to the white king. } 22. exd6
Rxc4
{ The idea of the entire sequence - Black wants to play ...Qb2+. White doesn't have a choice here. }
23. Qxc4 Qb2+ 24. Kd3
{ 24.Qc2  Re2+!  Black wins back the material with a little trick and remains ahead. }
24... Be4+ 25. Qxe4 Qa3+
{ The final accuracy - White loses the queen and Black's attack continues. } *

