15... O-O-O 16. Ba3 Rhe8
{ Black is threatening to win another pawn with more pressure against the white king. Now a human continuation would be  17.bxc4  Qxe5  18.Qxe5  Rxe5  19.Rhd1  and here Black has the amazing shot  19...Ne6!  and the knight on d3 is indirectly defended with ...Nf4+, plus Black is threatening with ...Ra5. }
