12. b4
{ With this burst White is not wasting time on slow moves like a3 and is immediately looking for some queenside activities. }
12... e4
{ Suddenly this looks like the most suitable approach of the two options. } 13.
dxe4 Nxe4 { The white b4 pawn feels a little weird. } 14. a3
{ 14.Nxb6  would trade-off too many pieces and pawns for White to hope for something real, for example,  14...axb6  15.Bf4  Qxd1  16.Rfxd1  Nxb4  and the a2 pawn is gone as well. }
14... Nxd2 15. Nxd2 Bg4 { Black is very active. } *

