15. Be5 Re8 16. Nxb6 axb6 17. Bxc7 Rxa2
{ In the game Vachier Lagrave, M @@StartBracket@@2779@@EndBracket@@-Carlsen, M @@StartBracket@@2875@@EndBracket@@ Norway Chess armageddon blitz 2019 Black was active enough to trade off everything and secure a draw after  18.Ne5  Bf5  19.Nxc6  bxc6  ,  and with the white b-pawn gone, White's chances to win the game evaporated. }
