{ Black already wants to play ...Nd4 next and recapture with the e-pawn. } 11.
Na4 Bb6
{ This would just transpose to some previously covered lines: A B C but given the order of the moves, Black can seriously consider positioning the dark-squared bishop on f8 instead. if Black considers this alternative:   11...Bf8  ,  Black wants to play ...Nd4 next, followed by ...c6. It will transpose to lines like this. }
